Title: Resolution of Singularities

Description:

resolution of singularities (Villamayor)

--

    Villamayor U., Orlando On constructive desingularization.  J. Symbolic Comput.
    39 (2005), no. 3-4, 465--491.

    http://front.math.ucdavis.edu/math.AG/0103120
    math.AG/0103120
    Title: Notes on the inductive algorithm of resolution of singularities by S. Encinas and O. Villamayor
    Author: Kenji Matsuki 

This algorithm has been implemented in Singular by Frühbis:

    Frühbis-Krüger, G. Pfister: Algorithmic Resolution of Singularities. In:
    C. Lossen and G. Pfister (eds.), Singularities and Computer Algebra. Lecture
    Notes of LMS, Cambridge University Press, to appear (2005/06).
    http://www.singular.uni-kl.de/publications.html

Integral closure should be done before we start on this.

